These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
City: liverpool, hamburg, rome, colone
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, october, april, july
1. the person traveling to hamburg is between the person traveling to liverpool and the person who's birthday is in october##2
2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
3. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere between the person traveling to colone and the person traveling to liverpool##7
4. the person who's birthday is in october is in an even position##4
5. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| City   | rome | colone       | hamburg | liverpool        |
| Birthday      | april  | october | july        | may |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, bike, boat, tram
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, country, techno, soul
1. the fan soul is somewhere between the fan techno and the person driving the boat##7
2. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##5
3. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the right of the fan soul##5
4. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
5. the fan soul is between the fan techno and the fan country##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Transport     | boat | bike       | tram         | jet-ski     |
| Music-Genre   | country   | soul | techno | trance |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, begonia, tulip, orchid
House: victorian, ranch-style, farmhouse, wooden
1. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the wooden house##1
2. the wooden house is somewhere between the ranch-style house and the victorian house##7
3. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
4. the victorian house is somewhere between the wooden house and the person who growsbegonia##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Flower   | begonia | orchid | tulip | bellflower  |
| House   | farmhouse | victorian  | wooden   | ranch-style |

