.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, blue, blood-red, orange
4 different games are played: backgammon, domino, monopoly, snooker
1. the person playing snooker is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who likes lilac is somewhere between the person playing domino and the person who likes orange##7
3. the person who likes blood-red is the person playing snooker##1
4. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
5. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Color   | blue | lilac | orange       | blood-red |
| Game   | domino      | backgammon   | monopoly | snooker  |

