.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
City: boston, venice, paris, liverpool
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, time-travel, family, musical
1. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
2. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##5
3. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
4. the person watching musical movies is somewhere between the person traveling to venice and the person traveling to boston##7
5. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
6. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching musical movies##5
7. the person traveling to venice is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| City         | paris | boston   | liverpool | venice |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery      | time-travel | musical      | family |

