.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, december, november, march
There 4 different types of food: onion, banana, tomato, avocado
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
2. the person eating tomato is the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the person eating banana is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person eating avocado##3
6. the person eating avocado is somewhere between the person eating onion and the person eating banana##7
7. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Birthday      | december | april      | november | march     |
| Food   | onion    | avocado | banana   | tomato |

