.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
City: hannover, nizza, marseilles, edinburgh
4 different games are played: poker, billiard, bridge, whist
1. the person playing poker is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person playing whist is somewhere between the person traveling to hannover and the person traveling to marseilles##7
5. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##5
6. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| City          | edinburgh    | hannover   | nizza | marseilles  |
| Game   | poker | bridge | whist    | billiard |

