.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, azure, aquamarine, lavender
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, van, jet-ski, taxi
1. the person who likes azure is not the person driving the taxi##6
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
3. the person who likes lavender is the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the person who likes aquamarine is somewhere between the person who likes lavender and the person who likes ebony##7
5. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
6. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
7. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Color   | lavender | aquamarine | azure | ebony |
| Transport           | jet-ski   | taxi    | subway       | van  |

