.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-9::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, siglo, blend, bluemaster
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, bus, snowmobile, motorbike
1. the oliveros-smoker is not the person driving the train##6
2. the blend-smoker is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
3. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3
4. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the blend-smoker is somewhere between the person driving the motorbike and the siglo-smoker##7
6. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Cigar           | bluemaster | oliveros | blend | siglo |
| Transport   | motorbike         | snowmobile      | train | bus            |

