.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, skateboarding, ice-hockey, lacrosse
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, grey, ivory, chestnut
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person who likes chestnut##7
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not the person who likes ivory##6
3. the person who likes grey is not the person who's sport is ice-hockey##6
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the right of the person who likes chestnut##5
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who likes lavender##1
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere to the right of the person who likes lavender##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Sport   | weightlifting | lacrosse | skateboarding | ice-hockey |
| Color           | lavender    | grey   | chestnut  | ivory      |

