.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-13::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, bartender, writer, firefighter
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, scientific, comedy, romance
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the security-guard##1
2. the firefighter is the person watching crime movies##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is the writer##1
4. the writer is not the person watching scientific movies##6
5. the writer is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
6. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the person watching crime movies and the writer##7
7. the bartender is somewhere to the left of the person watching comedy movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Job       | firefighter | security-guard | bartender | writer |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | romance      | scientific        | comedy  |

