.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-14::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, basketball, volleyball, sailing
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, malaysian, thai, brazilian
1. the malaysian is in an even position##4
2. the brazilian is somewhere between the person who's sport is sailing and the thai##7
3. the brazilian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
4. the thai is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the left of the malaysian##5
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the thai##1
7. the person who's sport is basketball is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Sport      | snowboarding   | volleyball | basketball | sailing   |
| Nationality   | indonesian | thai   | brazilian | malaysian |

