3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the modern house is somewhere to the left of the craftsman house##5
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
6. the wooden house is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |  3   |    4     |
| Hobby    | drawing   | woodworking  | filmmaking  | rock-climbing |
| House   | modern | colonial | craftsman | wooden    |

