.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, billiard, domino, poker
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, salsa, hip-hop, pop
1. the person playing domino is somewhere between the fan jazz and the person playing billiard##7
2. the fan jazz is on the right of the fan salsa##1
3. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the fan salsa is somewhere to the right of the person playing domino##5
5. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the fan hip-hop##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Game         | billiard    | domino | poker     | mah-jongg |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | pop  | salsa | jazz |

 